<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c37f397-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s2235"><num value="2235">§ 2235.</num><heading> Construction in usable increments</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any navigation project for a harbor or inland harbor authorized by this subchapter or any other provision of law enacted before, on, or after <date date="1986-11-17">November 17, 1986</date>, may be constructed in usable increments.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6c37f398-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/662/tII/s207">Pub. L. 99–662, title II, § 207</ref>, <date date="1986-11-17">Nov. 17, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/4102">100 Stat. 4102</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
